      <h2 class="h2">What sort of items will Nottingham Street Aid pay for?</h2>
      <p>The fund will pay for the following kind of items which help people to engage with support services, gain employment or move into accommodation.</p>
      <ul>
        <img class="notts-street-aid-logo" src="/assets/img/nottingham-logos/nottingham-street-aid.png" alt="notts street aid logo">
        <li>Bike (plus accessories)</li>
        <li>Travel (eg for interview)</li>
        <li>Training (eg for work)</li>
        <li>Laptop or tablet</li>
        <li>Phone</li>
        <li>Driving licence</li>
        <li>Clothes/suit/shoes</li>
        <li>White goods</li>
        <li>Bed</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This list is not exhaustive, and charities can apply for anything on behalf of their clients.</p>
